---
import ModuleLayout from '../../layouts/ModuleLayout.astro';
import { withBase } from '../../lib/utils';
---

<ModuleLayout moduleId="tian" title="天时">
  <div class="tian-overview">
    <section class="intro-section">
      <h2>天道运行之理</h2>
      <p>天者，万物之始也。日月星辰，循轨而行；春夏秋冬，周而复始。修行者观天象以知灵气潮汐，察节气以调身心之息。</p>
    </section>

    <section class="features-grid">
      <a href={withBase('/tian/calendar')} class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">📅</div>
        <h3>黄历吉凶</h3>
        <p>每日宜忌查询</p>
      </a>
      <a href={withBase('/tian/bazi')} class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🎴</div>
        <h3>八字排盘</h3>
        <p>生辰四柱推演</p>
      </a>
      <a href={withBase('/tian/stars')} class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">⭐</div>
        <h3>星辰运行</h3>
        <p>二十八宿星象</p>
      </a>
      <a href={withBase('/tian/solar-terms')} class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🌿</div>
        <h3>节气养生</h3>
        <p>节气与养生</p>
      </a>
      <a href={withBase('/tian/daily-quote')} class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">💫</div>
        <h3>每日吉言</h3>
        <p>每日箴言运势</p>
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="knowledge-section">
      <h2>天时知识</h2>
      <div class="knowledge-grid">
        <article class="knowledge-card">
          <h3>天干地支</h3>
          <p>天干十：甲乙丙丁戊己庚辛壬癸<br>地支十二：子丑寅卯辰巳午未申酉戌亥</p>
        </article>
        <article class="knowledge-card">
          <h3>五行与天象</h3>
          <p>金木水火土五行，对应五星：太白、岁星、辰星、荧惑、镇星。五星运行主四方吉凶。</p>
        </article>
        <article class="knowledge-card">
          <h3>灵气潮汐</h3>
          <p>月圆之夜灵气最盛，修行者多于此时吸收月华。日出时分阳气升腾，宜行吐纳之术。</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <style>
    .tian-overview {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .intro-section {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: rgba(240, 192, 64, 0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(240, 192, 64, 0.2);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .intro-section h2 {
      color: #f0c040;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .intro-section p {
      color: #888;
      line-height: 1.8;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .feature-card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      background: rgba(10, 10, 15, 0.8);
      border: 1px solid rgba(240, 192, 64, 0.2);
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      border-color: #f0c040;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(240, 192, 64, 0.15);
    }

    .card-icon {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .feature-card h3 {
      color: #f0e6c8;
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .feature-card p {
      color: #888;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    .knowledge-section h2 {
      color: #f0c040;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .knowledge-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .knowledge-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
      background: rgba(10, 10, 15, 0.6);
      border: 1px solid rgba(201, 162, 39, 0.1);
      border-radius: 6px;
    }

    .knowledge-card h3 {
      color: #c9a227;
      margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .knowledge-card p {
      color: #aaa;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  </style>
</ModuleLayout>
